{"tid":670581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[2018 05月19日]鴨寮街冚鹹碟舖　檢近6千色情光碟","createTime":"2018-05-19T13:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T11:03:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf9cd76471a49c976df091dd0f2e6797e80a98e","tid":670581,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"警方持續「雷霆18」反罪惡行動，下午約2時，深水埗警區特別職務隊探員，根據線報並深入調查後，展開代號「雷霆18」及「犁庭掃穴」反色情行動，探員喬裝顧客到鴨寮街一間懷疑售賣色情光碟店鋪「放蛇」，成功購買色情光碟，遂表露身份破該間鹹碟舖。<br />\n<br />\n警方以涉嫌「管有淫褻物品以供發布用途」及「發佈淫褻物品」，拘捕負責看舖的姓洪男子(43歲)。行動中，檢獲約<span style=\"color: red;\">5890隻懷疑色情光碟，市值約17萬元</span>，以及現金等證物，疑犯被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180519/bkn-20180519202835353-0519_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180519%2Fbkn-20180519202835353-0519_00822_001.html&d=sa1RKEo%2FZvI%2FYpjki5u47v1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=cbd32945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180519/bkn-20180519202835353-0519_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c9423d3ce480b883b5bd2eee6995da3cfd661a92","tid":670581,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:25:09.000Z","msg":"HK No IT<br />\n<br />\nHK Yes DVD player<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8fa88288e8da5230bbad46c71ae597e377dc24","tid":670581,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180519/photo/bkn-20180519202835353-0519_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180519212211\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180519%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180519202835353-0519_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180519212211&h=8cd72276&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"470dde6b870224e3a32b573b0b89b683aab5e866","tid":670581,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T13:28:53.000Z","